name: Super Techno Kitten Adventure
blurb: Everything we've always wanted Techno Kitten to be, plus everything else fans have asked us for. This will be the ultimate adventure!

rewards.reward: BACKER KITTEH: Get the game we're here supporting, Super Techno Kitten Adventure, for PC & MAC download upon release + Exclusive Wallpaper Pack in a variety of resolutions for Desktops, Tablets and Phones + We give you a virtual hug by adding your name to our Wall of Awezome on the official website and you help us all get closer to touching the blue blue sky :)

KLASSIC KITTEH: Previous Rewards + The original Techno Kitten Adventure for PC download including DREAM, LAVA, CLOUD & MEAT Packs. (This has never been available before and is not available anywhere else!!) + DRM Free MP3 of "Taste of Heavin" from the original TKA's Meat Pack

PARTY KITTEH: Previous Rewards + An advance download of the DRM Free Super Techno Kitten Adventure Soundtrack! Any TKA fan knows- it's all about the awesome music. New songs from S3RL, Fracus, R-KADE and many more! Get the full album before the game is released!

JETPACK KITTEH: Previous Rewards + The Limited Edition STKA Jetpack Kitteh T-shirt for you and in-game for your custom Kitteh. Printed & Downloadable for Kickstarter backers and never available again!

BETA KITTEH: Previous Rewards + The STKA BETA BUNDLE including: Early Beta access to the game on PC, Mac and iOS, membership in our STKA Beta Forums where you'll be able to communicate with the team throughout development & receive news, videos, art and previews before anyone else + YOUR NAME in the Beta Testers section of the actual game credits!! This is the reward for anyone who has dreamed about being involved in the creation of a video game.

ANGEL KITTEH: Previous Rewards + A limited edition physical copy of the game for PC & Mac featuring custom packaging & artwork + A gorgeous Hardcover STKA art book signed by the entire team, featuring an original sketch by one of the STKA artists right on the cover.

DANCE KITTEH: Previous Rewards + 2 copies of an extremely limited pressing of the STKA soundtrack on Rainbow vinyl. The team has taken great care to create a truly unique art piece for TKA and Music fans. Why do we give you 2 copies? So you can keep one in mint condition & play the other!

BYARF KITTEH: Previous Rewards + An Original framed piece of concept art by lead illustrator and Eisner Award Nominee, Rolo Ledesma. This is not a print or lithograph. This is original artwork used to create actual art assets within the game.

DREAM KITTEH: Previous Rewards + An Original 12"x12" canvas painting by STKA Art Director, Narek Gevorgian. This is not a print or a lithograph. This is an actual painting by the dude responsible for the pretty rainbows and cute kittehs you've come to love.

TECHNO KITTEH: Previous Rewards + You get to choose 3 background items to place into a level in STKA (upon approval). Work directly with our team to add your own personal touches into the TKA universe. Did you always want to see a rollerblading bee buzzing around one of TKA's backgrounds? Well, this is your chance to tell people, "See that bee? That was my idea." Dedicate the other two items to your friends or family- or don't- it's your call!

BACON KITTEH: Previous Rewards + Spend the day at 21st Street Games and work with our art team to create your own custom Kitteh that will be an official playable character in STKA (upon approval). Then join the team for a night out in your honor at Barcade if you're over 21 or Dave & Buster's if you're under 21. (1 Night Hotel in NYC included!)

SUPER KITTEH: Previous Rewards + Join the team for a night of glory with box seats at Yankees Stadium accompanied by a mystery celebrity (TBA)! Dine on sushi and hot dogs with game developers and a celeb in a suite at a baseball game! But wait, there's more! Super Kittehs also get an invite to one of Maxim's upcoming exclusive VIP parties. Past events have included Comic-Con, Super Bowl and Oscar parties. Talk about one-of-a-kind experiences! (2 Day/1 Night Travel expenses to NYC included!)
